===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-both}}

# (countable or uncountable) A [[quantity]] or [[volume]].
#:''Pour a small '''amount''' of water into the dish.''
#:''The dogs need different '''amounts''' of food.''
# (uncountable) The [[number]] of elements in a [[set]].

